---
// Stylized mockup of the JustWrite app window — pure HTML/CSS,
// no real screenshot required. Echoes the in-app chrome.
---
<div class="mockup" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="mockup-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="mockup-window">
    <div class="mockup-titlebar">
      <div class="dots">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="title">JustWrite — <em>The Quiet Hour</em></div>
      <div class="title-right"><span>⌘</span><span>F</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mockup-body">
      <aside class="mockup-side">
        <div class="m-brand"><span class="m-mark">J</span><span class="m-name">JustWrite</span></div>
        <div class="m-section">Manuscript</div>
        <ul>
          <li class="active"><span class="m-num">i.</span> Chapter One — Arrivals</li>
          <li><span class="m-num">ii.</span> Chapter Two — The Quiet Hour</li>
          <li><span class="m-num">iii.</span> Chapter Three — Confession</li>
          <li><span class="m-num">iv.</span> Chapter Four — A Letter Lost</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="m-section">World</div>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="m-dot c1"></span> Iris Mendel</li>
          <li><span class="m-dot c2"></span> Hollow House</li>
          <li><span class="m-dot c3"></span> Father's coat</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="m-section">Studio</div>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="m-mono">tts</span> Audiobook render</li>
          <li><span class="m-mono">srt</span> Captions</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>

      <article class="mockup-page">
        <div class="page-running">JUST · WRITE &nbsp; · &nbsp; CHAPTER ONE</div>
        <h2>Arrivals</h2>
        <div class="scene-mark">* * *</div>
        <p>
          <span class="dropcap">T</span>he train pulled in just after the bells, and Iris stepped down onto a platform that smelled of rain and unsold flowers. She had imagined this town for so long that she could not, at first, believe it was real — that the hills were exactly the colour she had been writing them, and that the lamp by the station door was, indeed, the lamp.
        </p>
        <p>
          A man in a grey coat watched her without curiosity. He had been waiting for someone else.
        </p>
        <p>
          She turned up her collar. The river smelled of old paper.
        </p>
      </article>

      <aside class="mockup-meta">
        <div class="m-meta-block">
          <div class="m-meta-label">Session</div>
          <div class="m-meta-value"><strong>1,284</strong> words</div>
          <div class="m-meta-bar"><span style="width:64%"></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-meta-block">
          <div class="m-meta-label">Streak</div>
          <div class="m-meta-value"><em>9 days</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-meta-block">
          <div class="m-meta-label">Status</div>
          <div class="m-meta-pill">Draft</div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-meta-block">
          <div class="m-meta-label">AI</div>
          <div class="m-meta-mono">ollama / llama3.1</div>
          <div class="m-meta-mono dim">openai / gpt-4o-mini</div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mockup {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    isolation: isolate;
    transform: perspective(2400px) rotateX(2deg);
    transform-origin: 50% 100%;
  }
  .mockup-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -8% -6% -10% -6%;
    border-radius: 32px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 60% at 30% 20%, oklch(0.62 0.12 14 / 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(50% 50% at 80% 80%, oklch(0.62 0.10 320 / 0.18), transparent 60%);
    filter: blur(40px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .mockup-window {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-deep);
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .mockup-titlebar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 14px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-2), var(--surface-3));
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
  .dots { display: flex; gap: 7px; }
  .dots span {
    width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border-strong);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .dots span:nth-child(1) { background: oklch(0.72 0.12 25); }
  .dots span:nth-child(2) { background: oklch(0.78 0.12 80); }
  .dots span:nth-child(3) { background: oklch(0.72 0.09 145); }

  .title {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .title em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
  .title-right {
    display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .title-right span {
    display: inline-grid; place-items: center;
    min-width: 18px; height: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .mockup-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 180px;
    min-height: 440px;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .mockup-side {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
  .m-brand {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .m-mark {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), oklch(0.52 0.10 320));
    color: white; display: grid; place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;
  }
  .m-name { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }

  .m-section {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 14px 4px 6px;
  }
  .mockup-side ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px;
  }
  .mockup-side li {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 5px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
  .mockup-side li.active {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent-ink);
  }
  .m-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 11px;
    min-width: 18px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .mockup-side li.active .m-num { color: var(--accent); }
  .m-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .m-dot.c1 { background: oklch(0.72 0.10 25); }
  .m-dot.c2 { background: oklch(0.72 0.08 145); }
  .m-dot.c3 { background: oklch(0.72 0.08 270); }
  .m-mono {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    padding: 1px 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  /* Manuscript page */
  .mockup-page {
    padding: 28px 36px 44px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(400px 240px at 50% 0%, oklch(0.99 0.005 85 / 0.6), transparent 70%),
      var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  html[data-theme="dark"] .mockup-page {
    background:
      radial-gradient(400px 240px at 50% 0%, oklch(0.28 0.008 80 / 0.5), transparent 70%),
      var(--paper);
  }
  .page-running {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    color: var(--subtle);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .mockup-page h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }
  .scene-mark {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.7em;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 18px 0 22px;
  }
  .mockup-page p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
    text-indent: 1.6em;
  }
  .mockup-page p:first-of-type { text-indent: 0; }
  .mockup-page p + p { margin-top: 0.3em; }
  .dropcap {
    float: left;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 3.2em;
    line-height: 0.82;
    margin: 0.05em 0.09em -0.08em 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Meta column */
  .mockup-meta {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px 14px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .m-meta-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .m-meta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .m-meta-value {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .m-meta-value strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .m-meta-value em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .m-meta-bar {
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--surface-3);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .m-meta-bar span {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--gold));
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .m-meta-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .m-meta-mono {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .m-meta-mono.dim { color: var(--subtle); }

  /* Responsive collapse */
  @media (max-width: 920px) {
    .mockup-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mockup-side, .mockup-meta { display: none; }
    .mockup-page { padding: 20px 22px 32px; }
  }
</style>
